    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Furry3.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/Furry3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637969\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Furry3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f96d099e-3108-4626-8db5-dc7fe65d3575\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>The RenderMan Curve primitive is a great geometry type for rendering hair and fur, as it’s designed to render a multitude of very thin strands efficiently.</p><p>See <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661233/Curves\" rel=\"nofollow\">Curves</a> for more information.</p><p /><h2 id=\"Curves-CurveTypes\">Curve Types</h2><p>RfB should be able to render most curve types in Blender. However, not all settings may be supported.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"curves_render.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=433\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/curves_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1198\" data-width=\"2098\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637978\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"curves_render.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f9608599-025c-4fe1-a687-53f6ad1f6eb4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=866 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=433 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"Curves-CurveWidths\">Curve Widths</h2><p>If you want to vary the width of your curve, you can do so by selecting your object and going to Edit Mode. Select the vertex you want to change the width, and change the radius setting.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"widths_edit_mode2.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/widths_edit_mode2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=434\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/widths_edit_mode2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1211\" data-width=\"2120\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637975\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"widths_edit_mode2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"272758fd-a929-4b4a-ab27-feb621deb56a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/widths_edit_mode2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=868 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/widths_edit_mode2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697926&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=434 1x\"></span><p>And, here’s an example render:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"curves_render2.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=435\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/curves_render2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1213\" data-width=\"2118\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637972\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"curves_render2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f9584246-36cd-4934-8ad8-da1acb546bde\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=870 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/curves_render2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=435 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"Curves-RenderingandShadingCurves\">Rendering and Shading Curves</h2><p>Curves are best shaded with PxrMarschnerHair or LamaHairChiang materials. To color or texture curves, use a PxrHairColor pattern, which provides options for melanin, dye, strand variation, and more.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0bc055e0-7fe9-48a7-95d1-01e92174bf89\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>To add variation to your materials, use the <strong>index</strong> primvar in PxrhairColor &gt; hairIndexPrimvar attribute.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"FurryInterface.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=240\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/FurryInterface.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1216\" data-width=\"3838\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637960\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"FurryInterface.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ec600998-8c57-42e3-9654-f818ab3bd98f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=480 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=240 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"FurryInterface2.JPG\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=284\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/FurryInterface2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"730\" data-width=\"1947\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637957\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"FurryInterface2.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8cf98220-360e-48ae-9b9c-8748cc2c0f0d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=568 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/FurryInterface2.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=284 1x\"></span><hr/><p>A few fun example renders!</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Furry2.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/Furry2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637966\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Furry2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"632cc30e-73b9-415f-9d46-1c7f8e76c29f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Furry1.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637943/Furry1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637963\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Furry1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637943\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d270fe03-71e6-44c0-a04b-29191a5666a0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637943/Furry1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432697548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p />"
